Arguments

sabs

(optional) Comma-separated list of source vocabularies to include in your search
ttys

(optional) One or more term types
language

(optional) 3-letter abbreviation for language
includeObsolete

(optional) Determines whether to return obsolete codes.
includeSuppressible

(optional) Include content that is suppressible according to NLM Editors.
pageNumber

(optional) Whole number that specifies which page of results to fetch.
pageSize

(optional) Whole number that specifies the number of results to include per page.
includeRelationLabels

(optional) One or more relation labels
includeAdditionalRelationLabels

(optional) One or more relation attribute
includeAttributeNames

(optional) One or more attribute names
targetSource

(optional) Returns codes from the specified UMLS vocabulary
ticket

A single-use service ticket is required for each call to the API. See authentication for more information
